  "anki": "<div class=\"modal-header\"><button data-dismiss=\"modal\" class=\"close\" type=\"button\">×</button><img src=\"logo/anki.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"pull-left favlogo\" height=\"36\" ><h3>Anki<small class=\"service-url\">Share review <input class=\"share-link\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://tosdr.org/#anki\" readonly /></small></h3></div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"><div class=\"tosdr-rating\"><label class=\"label false\">No Class Yet</label><p>We haven't sufficiently reviewed the terms yet. Please contribute to our group: <a href=\"get-involved.html\">Get involved</a>.</p></div>\n<section class=\"specificissues\"> <ul class=\"tosdr-points\"><li id=\"popup-point-anki-5973\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> There is a date of the last update of the terms <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5973\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-anki-5974\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> The service may change its terms at any time, but the user will receive notification of the changes. <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5974\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></section>\n<section><a href=\"/get-involved.html\" class=\"btn\">Help us find the Terms »</a></section>\n</div>",
