  "evaneos": "<div class=\"modal-header\"><button data-dismiss=\"modal\" class=\"close\" type=\"button\">×</button><img src=\"logo/evaneos.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"pull-left favlogo\" height=\"36\" ><h3>Evaneos<small class=\"service-url\">Share review <input class=\"share-link\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://tosdr.org/#evaneos\" readonly /></small></h3></div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"><div class=\"tosdr-rating\"><label class=\"label false\">No Class Yet</label><p>We haven't sufficiently reviewed the terms yet. Please contribute to our group: <a href=\"get-involved.html\">Get involved</a>.</p></div>\n<section class=\"specificissues\"> <ul class=\"tosdr-points\"><li id=\"popup-point-evaneos-7172\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> Users can access most of the pages on the service's website without revealing any personal information <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/7172\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-evaneos-7175\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> The service provides information about how they collect personal data <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/7175\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-evaneos-7178\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> The service's data retention period is kept to the minimum necessary for fulfilling its purposes <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/7178\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-evaneos-7173\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> The service provides details about what kinds of personal information they collect <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/7173\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-evaneos-7176\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> The service provides information about how they intend to use your personal data <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/7176\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-evaneos-7179\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> You can opt out of promotional communications <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/7179\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></section>\n<section><a href=\"/get-involved.html\" class=\"btn\">Help us find the Terms »</a></section>\n</div>",
