  "freeforums": "<div class=\"modal-header\"><button data-dismiss=\"modal\" class=\"close\" type=\"button\">×</button><img src=\"logo/freeforums.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"pull-left favlogo\" height=\"36\" ><h3>Freeforums<small class=\"service-url\">Share review <input class=\"share-link\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://tosdr.org/#freeforums\" readonly /></small></h3></div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"><div class=\"tosdr-rating\"><label class=\"label false\">No Class Yet</label><p>We haven't sufficiently reviewed the terms yet. Please contribute to our group: <a href=\"get-involved.html\">Get involved</a>.</p></div>\n<section class=\"specificissues\"> <ul class=\"tosdr-points\"><li id=\"popup-point-freeforums-1046\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span>  Terms may be changed any time at their discretion, without notice to the user  <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/1046\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>From http://www.freeforums.org/tos.php: \"FreeForums.org reserves the right to change the terms, conditions, and notices at any time, and such modifications shall be effective immediately upon posting of such changes.\"</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></section>\n<section><h4>Read the Terms</h4><ul class=\"tosback2\">\n<li><a href=\"http://www.crowdgather.com/legal/\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n</ul></section>\n</div>",
