  "linkedin": "<div class=\"modal-header\"><button data-dismiss=\"modal\" class=\"close\" type=\"button\">×</button><img src=\"logo/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"pull-left favlogo\" height=\"36\" ><h3>LinkedIn<small class=\"service-url\">Share review <input class=\"share-link\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://tosdr.org/#linkedin\" readonly /></small></h3></div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"><div class=\"tosdr-rating\"><label class=\"label false\">No Class Yet</label><p>We haven't sufficiently reviewed the terms yet. Please contribute to our group: <a href=\"get-involved.html\">Get involved</a>.</p></div>\n<section class=\"specificissues\"> <ul class=\"tosdr-points\"><li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5885\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service keeps user logs for an undefined period of time <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5885\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5896\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"blocker\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-important\" title=\"blocker\"><i class=\"icon-remove icon-white\">×</i></span> Your identity is used in ads that are shown to other users <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5896\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5886\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service may collect, use, and share location data <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5886\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5892\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service allows tracking via third-party cookies for purposes including targeted advertising. <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5892\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5891\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service ignores the Do Not Track (DNT) header and tracks users anyway even if they set this header. <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5891\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5881\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> The service has a no refund policy <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5881\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5887\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> The service may use tracking pixels, web beacons, browser fingerprinting, and/or device fingerprinting on users. <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5887\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5888\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> You can delete your content from this service <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5888\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5894\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> The service can sell or otherwise transfer your personal data as part of a bankruptcy proceeding or other type of financial transaction. <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5894\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5895\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"blocker\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-important\" title=\"blocker\"><i class=\"icon-remove icon-white\">×</i></span> The service can delete specific content without prior notice and without a reason <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5895\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5918\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service can use your content for all their existing and future services <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5918\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5884\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service uses your personal information for many different purposes <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5884\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5889\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> This service provides a way for you to export your data <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5889\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5893\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"blocker\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-important\" title=\"blocker\"><i class=\"icon-remove icon-white\">×</i></span> This service holds onto content that you've deleted <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5893\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5882\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> Users are not allowed to use pseudonyms, as trust and transparency between users regarding their identities is relevant to the service. <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5882\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5883\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> no spidering or crawling <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5883\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-linkedin-5880\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> The service may change its terms at any time, but the user will receive notification of the changes. <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/5880\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></section>\n<section><h4>Read the Terms</h4><ul class=\"tosback2\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/legal/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/legal/user-agreement\">Terms of Service</a></li>\n</ul></section>\n</div>",
