  "mrichard333": "<div class=\"modal-header\"><button data-dismiss=\"modal\" class=\"close\" type=\"button\">×</button><img src=\"logo/mrichard333.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"pull-left favlogo\" height=\"36\" ><h3>MRichard333<small class=\"service-url\">Share review <input class=\"share-link\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://tosdr.org/#mrichard333\" readonly /></small></h3></div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"><div class=\"tosdr-rating\"><label class=\"label false\">No Class Yet</label><p>We haven't sufficiently reviewed the terms yet. Please contribute to our group: <a href=\"get-involved.html\">Get involved</a>.</p></div>\n<section class=\"specificissues\"> <ul class=\"tosdr-points\"><li id=\"popup-point-mrichard333-7523\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> No Trackers & Privacy Focused <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/7523\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>We use cookies to provide you with a better online experience,Your Privacy is more important then everything, Data are Encrypted and Shred Regularly, Plus they're only stored Locally.\r\nBy visiting our Website you allow us to Collect and Process Data.\r\n\r\n        Privacy Policy\r\n\r\n- NO Trackers!\r\n\r\n- The High level of Privacy\r\n\r\n- Less Data Collection then Google (Eazy)\r\n\r\n- Respect of your Privacy</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></section>\n<section><a href=\"/get-involved.html\" class=\"btn\">Help us find the Terms »</a></section>\n</div>",
